                <p>AI assistants can connect to this server at  <code>https://ai.jakegaylor.com/mcp</code> to learn more about me and my work.</p>
                <p>To connect to this server with tools that do not support remote MCP servers, you can use the following command:</p>
                <pre><code>npx -y @jhgaylor/me-mcp</code></pre>
                <p>See <a href="#connection-instructions">below</a> for detailed connection instructions.</p>
            </section>

